column5: Not sure if she,s rubb,n it in or just being nice.I told her I have a few days left still to get one.  TY hun.  My new chair blankie
I'm tellin Santa, not suppose to open till Christmas morning.
Nice blanket you got. Closest you've been to a deer in a while?? 	All right, enough picking on ya.
That would make a great practice target!
